Name of the program: Adventures
This is a text based italian adventures creator for all Amigas with a lot of
memory.
By itself does not do a lot, but it can be useful if you don't want to make your
adventures generator starting from zero.
There are the original AMOS Professional source code and its text version to
meet the needs of the people that do not have AMOS Professional also.
These source codes can be freely modified, on condition that you mention me in
your resulting final program.
I am not responsible of any damage these programs can occur to your system; you
use them at your own risk!
I have removed the executable from the archive because it doesn't want to run
neither on my AMIGA 1200 that now has 128 Megs of Fast RAM nor under my PC using
WinUAE that also has 128 Megs of memory at its disposal!
Now there is the source code in text format so everybody can see it.
